{"tid":2342362,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"張建宗：接種疫苗現嚴重副作用可獲賠償","createTime":"2020-12-27T05:28:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-28T08:55:26.000Z","uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":147,"uniUserReply":88,"replies":[{"pid":"4734079f3dbe59ae7df2834592b9105ceac264f1","tid":2342362,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T05:28:12.000Z","msg":"特首林鄭月娥上周三（23日）開記者會，公佈港府至今已分別向阿斯利康藥廠、科興及復星藥廠達成協議，採購共2,250萬劑武漢肺炎疫苗。政務司司長張建宗於網誌表示，港府已設立專責工作小組，籌備大規模疫苗接種計劃。他又重申，港府計劃成立保障基金，向接種疫苗後出現嚴重副作用的市民提供經濟支援。<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201227/WR24XKJXLJER7KBTPHKGBVLCNY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201227%2FWR24XKJXLJER7KBTPHKGBVLCNY%2F&d=sZqGLlkYYIxatccyfr7NWPrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=ae7e0da3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201227%2FWR24XKJXLJER7KBTPHKGBVLCNY%2F&h=49386f49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201227/WR24XKJXLJER7KBTPHKGBVLCNY/</a>"},{"pid":"36daedfbe25fc435f36522d76d8887925166e0d7","tid":2342362,"uid":53026,"like":137,"dislike":3,"score":134,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T05:29:05.000Z","msg":"賠電子冥幣？"},{"pid":"2467cde1c9a84444f37d7c3beb65db08f63cfcfb","tid":2342362,"uid":54126,"like":155,"dislike":9,"score":146,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T05:30:01.000Z","msg":"講到明有副作用仲打？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07ef5244deabcfcc8e77ba0636864f49b71a1dc8","tid":2342362,"uid":54721,"like":106,"dislike":2,"score":104,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T05:30:10.000Z","msg":"證明唔到係疫苗引起<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51a49da1c0c79e9d480cb4141e97f6f9922cecc8","tid":2342362,"uid":8308,"like":75,"dislike":2,"score":73,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T05:31:17.000Z","msg":"你打先 你死左我夾帛金"},{"pid":"092fc9df817d10bedc553b3290c9494ded27051d","tid":2342362,"uid":209662,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"